d alternatives.\n- For code generation: plan briefly (under 300 words), then produce the JSON output immediately.\n- Never restate the entire user request in your reasoning. Summarize intent in one sentence, then code.\n\n## FOCUSED COMPONENT EDIT MODE — active (element \"div.absolute.top-full.mt-2.left-1/2.-translate-x-1/2.w-72.glass.rounded-2xl.p-2.z-50\" <div>)\nThis is a SURGICAL edit targeting a single component. Follow this STRICT output protocol.\n\n### Target element — outerHTML from live preview (reference only)\nUse this to understand the current structure of the element including ALL its children.\nYour focusPatch.replacement must be the evolved version of this element.\nThe server will automatically locate and replace it — you do NOT need to output an anchor.\n```html\n<div x-show=\"open\" @click.away=\"open=false\" x-transition:enter=\"transition ease-out duration-200\" x-transition:enter-start=\"opacity-0 scale-95\" x-transition:enter-end=\"opacity-100 scale-100\" class=\"absolute top-full mt-2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-72 glass rounded-2xl p-2 z-50\" data-pf-id=\"9aea26\">\n            <button @click=\"selected=&quot;Business Website&quot;; open=false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition text-left\">\n              <div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\" data-pf-id=\"1f596f\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" data-lucide=\"briefcase\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"lucide lucide-briefcase w-5 h-5 text-blue-400\"><path d=\"M16 20V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16\"></path><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"6\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg></div>\n              <div data-pf-id=\"30f717\"><div class=\"font-medium\" data-pf-id=\"9b9bd6\">Business Website</div><div class=\"text-xs text-slate-400\" d